WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.660
I told you, you need to truly know me first.

2
00:00:03.660 --> 00:00:07.139
I'm willing to change.

3
00:00:07.139 --> 00:00:10.539
I want to spend the rest of my life getting to know you.

4
00:00:10.539 --> 00:00:12.460
You're part of me.

5
00:00:12.460 --> 00:00:29.690
I can't bear to lose you.

6
00:00:29.690 --> 00:00:33.689
I understand now that we both need equality and freedom.

7
00:00:33.689 --> 00:00:44.000
And if you were to get hurt, or if you were to die

8
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:52.909
by your own actions, then I'm just going to have to learn to accept it.

9
00:00:52.909 --> 00:00:59.020
If you die, we die together.

10
00:00:59.020 --> 00:01:04.099
I made a promise that the Black Wedding, a blood oath,

11
00:01:04.099 --> 00:01:07.579
I'll stand by it.

12
00:01:07.579 --> 00:01:09.769
To love and to cherish.

13
00:01:09.769 --> 00:01:11.769
To death to his part.

14
00:01:11.769 --> 00:01:15.439
I wrote the beginning of our story.

15
00:01:15.439 --> 00:01:17.439
You're going to write the ending, okay?

